<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include("templates/head", {title: "Mario Hanina"}); %>

<body>

    <%- include("templates/navbar") -%>

    <!-- Profile Section -->
    <section id="intro">
        <div class="max-width-800 middle">
            <h1 class="text-center">Hello visitor, I'm Mario.</h1>
            <div class="intro-wrapper">
                <img class="profile-picture border" src="images/profile.jpg" alt="A picture of Me">
                <div class="profile-text m-b-0">
                    <span>I'm just another human.</span>
                    <p class="m-b-0">I created this website to share with you some
                        of the highlights of my life, the creations of my imagination, and the activities that I
                        enjoy doing.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Art Section -->
    <section id="hobbies">
        <h2 class="text-center">Hobbies</h2>
        <div class="hobby-categories">
            <!-- Dry Media -->
            <div class="hobby-wrapper">
                <a href="/hobbies/art-gallery">
                    <div class="hobby-cards">
                        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvn8e9cgl/image/upload/w_500/v1719780684/big-bear-lodge_cxoxpr.jpg"
                            alt="One of my drawings">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Drawing and Painting</h3>
                </a>
                <p>I draw because I want to materialize my thoughts, my interpretations, and my observations of the
                    world.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Photography -->
            <div class="hobby-wrapper">
                <a href="/hobbies/photo-gallery">
                    <div class="hobby-cards">
                        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvn8e9cgl/image/upload/w_500/v1719724180/lake-moraine_muqedk.jpg"
                            alt="One of my photographs">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Traveling</h3>
                </a>
                <p>Like most humans, I enjoy capturing fleeting moments. You might enjoy seeing the world through my
                    eyes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Apps -->
    <section id="software">
        <h2 class="text-center">Software</h2>
        <div class="hobby-categories">
            <!-- Flashcards -->
            <div class="hobby-wrapper">
                <a href="/flashcards-app">
                    <div class="hobby-cards">
                        <img src="images/software/flashcards.png" alt="Flashcards app">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Flashcards app</h3>
                </a>
                <p>I wrote this software to practice my Spanish Vocabulary,
                    you can practice yours too if you want.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Stocks App -->
            <div class="hobby-wrapper">
                <a href="/stocks-app">
                    <div class="hobby-cards">
                        <img src="images/software/stocks.png" alt="Stocks app">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Stocks app</h3>
                </a>
                <p>Use it to lookup the stock prices of different companies. This app is
                    limited since I'm using a free data source.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact -->
    <section id="contact">
        <h2 class="text-center">Contact me</h2>
        <form class="contact-form" action="/" method="post" target="_blank">
            <label for="email">Email: </label>
            <input type="text" id="email" name="email" required>

            <label for="phoneNumber">Phone Number: </label>
            <input type="text" id="phoneNumber" name="phoneNumber">

            <label for="subject">Subject: </label>
            <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject">

            <label for="message">Message: </label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>

            <button type="submit">Send</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <%- include("templates/copyright", {
        liSrc: "images/logos/linkedin.png", 
        ghSrc: "images/logos/github.png"
    }); %>

</body>

</html>